OL,3,CHospice forced to reduce beds and cut
OL,4,C45 full-time roles amid funding crisis
OL,6,FBirmingham Hospice is making staff
OL,7,Fredundant and reducing its number of
OL,8,Fbeds amid a funding crisis.
OL,10,FIn a statement the hospice said:
OL,11,F"Birmingham Hospice has today (27
OL,12,FJune) announced that it is proposing
OL,13,Fto make significant redundancies as it
OL,14,Ffaces unsustainable rising costs and
OL,15,Fan estimated #2.4 million deficit
OL,16,Fbudget this year."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/13
