OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F376A1719607638
OL,3,CHospice forced to reduce beds and cut
OL,4,C45 full-time roles amid funding crisis
OL,6,FThe hospice says it is experiencing
OL,7,Fsimilar challenges to other hospices
OL,8,Facross the country including the price
OL,9,Fof energy, food and drugs ` and the
OL,10,Ffunding it receives from the NHS has
OL,11,Fnot risen at the same rate.
OL,13,FSimon Fuller, CEO of Birmingham
OL,14,FHospice, said: "The prospect of having
OL,15,Fto make highly skilled specialist end
OL,16,Fof life clinicians and support staff
OL,17,Fredundant is totally unpalatable. We
OL,18,Fare doing everything we can to support
OL,19,Fall our hospice colleagues through
OL,20,Fthis difficult time.
OL,26,@vD@POU
