OL,6,FLucy Watkins, Income Generation
OL,7,FDirector at Birmingham Hospice, said:
OL,8,F"I'd like to thank those in the
OL,9,Fcommunity who have supported us over
OL,10,Fmany years. We need your support now
OL,11,Fmore than ever, and this year saw the
OL,12,Flaunch of our Crisis Appeal which has
OL,13,Fonce again seen people give what they
OL,14,Fcan to help us."
