OL,3,CHospice forced to reduce beds and cut
OL,4,C45 full-time roles amid funding crisis
OL,6,FDawn Ward, Chair of the Board of
OL,7,FTrustees for Birmingham Hospice,
OL,8,Fadded: "The hospice sector helps to
OL,9,Ftake pressure off the NHS by
OL,10,Fsupporting those with a terminal
OL,11,Fdiagnosis as inpatients or in the
OL,12,Fcommunity. If hospices are forced to
OL,13,Freduce the number of people they can
OL,14,Fhelp, that will mean longer stays and
OL,15,Fdelayed discharges from the acute
OL,16,Fsector, causing longer waits for
OL,17,Ftreatment elsewhere."
