OL,3,CHospice forced to reduce beds and cut
OL,4,C45 full-time roles amid funding crisis
OL,6,FToby Porter, CEO, Hospice UK said:
OL,7,F"This is devastating news for
OL,8,FBirmingham Hospice and for communities
OL,9,Facross the West Midlands.
OL,11,F"We all know our health and social
OL,12,Fcare system is under financial
OL,13,Fpressure. But even in difficult times,
OL,14,Fredundancies on this scale in
OL,15,Fmaternity services, in dentistry or in
OL,16,FGP practices would just not be
OL,17,Faccepted. Full stop.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/13
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
