OL,3,CHospice forced to reduce beds and cut
OL,4,C45 full-time roles amid funding crisis
OL,6,F"And yet here we are. Services for
OL,7,Fthose at the end of life in our second
OL,8,Fcity being cut back, because the way
OL,9,Fthey are funded is simply not working.
OL,11,F"We have seen encouraging commitments
OL,12,Fin party manifestos. But it's a matter
OL,13,Fof time before cuts like this spread
OL,14,Facross the country. Whoever forms the
OL,15,Fgovernment at the end of next week
OL,16,Fmust act."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/13
