OL,3,CHospice forced to reduce beds and cut
OL,4,C45 full-time roles amid funding crisis
OL,6,F"We recognise and value the services
OL,7,Fthat Birmingham Hospice offer to
OL,8,Fpatients. End of life care is critical
OL,9,Fboth in terms of enabling patients to
OL,10,Fdie in a place of their choosing and
OL,11,Fto ensuring that there is capacity in
OL,12,Four hospitals.
