OL,3,CHospice forced to reduce beds and cut
OL,4,C45 full-time roles amid funding crisis
OL,6,F"Since the inception of the ICB in
OL,7,FJuly 2022, funding for Birmingham
OL,8,FHospice has grown by #508,000,
OL,9,Fequivalent to a 5.9% funding increase
OL,10,Fand that is set against the limited
OL,11,Fadditional funding made available for
OL,12,Fthe NHS. In 23/24, the NHS in
OL,13,FBirmingham and Solihull made an
OL,14,Fadditional non-recurrent #858,000
OL,15,Favailable to Birmingham Hospice to
OL,16,Fmaintain capacity and support
OL,17,Fsustainability. We support 5 hospices
OL,18,Facross Birmingham and Solihull and
OL,19,Fcover a significantly higher
OL,20,Fpercentage of costs at Birmingham
OL,21,FHospice than at any other.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
